vertical column that is 25 feet in diameter (centred on the target
hex), with a height equal to the spell's range) must resist or suffer
[D - 4] (+1 / Rank) damage.  The Adept may counterspell this spell at
any time prior to the meteorite shower arriving by casting the
appropriate counterspell at the targeted hex.  The targeted hex will
have a magical aura until the meteorite shower arrives (or is
counterspelled by the Adept).  This spell will have no effect if it
is targeted on a hex which is already a target of this spell.  Note
that a solid surface (such as 10' of earth) will prevent the meteorite
shower from reaching its target hex.
