@d343 8
a350 9
\begin{effects} This spell gives the target the ability to
automatically see normally invisible entities or objects, or those
which have been rendered invisible by magic (\eg Blending, Walking
Unseen, E \& E Invisibility, etc).  These entities or objects, when
viewed, will appear to be surrounded by a faint blue glow.  It also
gives the target the night vision of an elf, which enables the target
to see as per a human on a cloudy day up to a range of 150' outdoors
or 75' elsewhere.  This spell will not give vision to an otherwise
sightless (or blinded) entity.
