to see at all at ranks 16--20.  Note that although light is being
banished, light can actually pass through the volume so it is not
possible for the volume to cast a shadow.  Only magical light sources
will be able to illuminate the volume.  Any or all of this volume can
be overridden by a Spell of Light.
